To run qooxdoo:
* Modern Browser:
  
  officially supported are
  - Internet Explorer 6.0
  - Mozilla >= 1.7
  - Opera >= 8

  also should work:
  - Internet Explorer 5.5
  - Mozilla >= 1.3
  - Opera >= 7.2
  - Safari >= 1.2

----------------------------------------------------------------------

To compile documentation and build a full qooxdoo package:
* bash
* python

----------------------------------------------------------------------

To build self configured qooxdoo dist packages
* perl
* perl-modules:
  - XML-NamespaceSupport
  - XML-SAX
  - Storable
  - Test-Harness
  - Test-Simple
  - XML-Simple

